---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-border" style="background: var(--color-capital-dark);">
  <div class="container py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-10">
      <!-- Brand -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xl text-white mb-4">Ummah.be Waqf</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Kapitaal is heilig. Opbrengsten dienen moslims. Voor altijd.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Links -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Navigatie</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/wat-is-een-waqf" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Wat is een Waqf?</a></li>
          <li><a href="/governance" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Governance</a></li>
          <li><a href="/transparantie" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Transparantie</a></li>
          <li><a href="/moskeeen" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Moskeeën</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Actie -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Steun</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/steun-ons" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Draag bij aan Kapitaal</a></li>
          <li><a href="/steun-ons" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Steun Programma's</a></li>
          <li><a href="/steun-ons" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Geef Zakat</a></li>
          <li><a href="/contact" class="text-white/60 hover:text-white no-underline transition-colors">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Legal -->
      <div>
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white/80 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4">Juridisch</h4>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
          Ummah.be Waqf is een Belgische waqf — eeuwig kapitaal in dienst van de Ummah.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/40 mt-4">
          Alle rechten voorbehouden.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="border-t border-white/10 mt-12 pt-6 text-center">
      <p class="text-xs text-white/30">&copy; {year} Ummah.be Waqf — Ummah.be Waqf</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
